snippet.title: it feels really good having you inside me [humor] | felicity/oliver
snippet.description:
if you'd like to support me, donate to my paypal: https://paypal.me/simplymaterial
"and by you I mean your voice, and by me I mean my ear. I'm going to stop talking, right now."

felicity smoak is literally the light of my life. gotta love babbling baby felicity and oliver's adorable smile in reaction to her. decided a humor video was a good idea, so this is basically a felicity smoak comedy apprecation.

*yes, I know about the echo. this was made a couple of years ago, I realise now that it's way too much. if I could change it I would, but I can't so, deal with it or exit the video and move on.
